  "remarks": "Nikolay Ovchinnikov is the General Director of Russian military industry company Zavod no 9. The company manufactures towed guns, including the D-30A howitzer, and tank guns for T-62, T-72 and T-90 tanks. D-30 howitzers and T-62, T-72 and T-90 tanks are\nused by the Russian Armed Forces during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Moreover, the company is a supplier of the Russian Armed Forces.",
